---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="HullSafe privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your personal data. GDPR compliant.">

  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="legal-content">

        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>HullSafe ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal data when you use our website (hullsafe.co.uk) and services.</p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following information when you use our booking forms or contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name, email address, and phone number</li>
          <li>Boat details (length, location, berth number)</li>
          <li>Booking preferences and service history</li>
          <li>Messages and correspondence</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We also automatically collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
          <li>Referring website</li>
          <li>IP address (anonymised where possible)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>We use your data to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Process and confirm bookings</li>
          <li>Deliver hull cleaning and inspection services</li>
          <li>Send service reports and documentation</li>
          <li>Communicate about your booking or enquiry</li>
          <li>Send marketing communications (only with your consent)</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
        <p>We process your data under the following legal bases (UK GDPR):</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contract:</strong> Processing necessary to fulfil our service agreement with you</li>
          <li><strong>Consent:</strong> Where you have given clear consent for us to contact you for marketing</li>
          <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> To improve our services and respond to enquiries</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share it with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Form processing services (to handle booking submissions)</li>
          <li>Website analytics providers (anonymised data only)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your personal data for as long as necessary to provide our services and comply with legal obligations. Booking records are retained for 6 years for tax and business purposes. You can request deletion at any time.</p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Rectify inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Restrict processing</li>
          <li>Data portability</li>
          <li>Object to processing</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses essential cookies for functionality. We do not currently use third-party tracking cookies. If this changes, we will update this policy and provide a cookie consent mechanism.</p>

        <h2>9. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any privacy-related queries, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@hullsafe.co.uk">hello@hullsafe.co.uk</a></p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    padding: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-3xl)) 0 var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--primary);
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .legal-hero h1 { color: var(--white); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .legal-hero p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

  .legal-content h2 { margin-top: var(--space-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .legal-content p { color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
  .legal-content ul { margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg) var(--space-xl); color: var(--text-light); }
  .legal-content li { margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
</style>
